title: Megastructures - Mega Plane, Galaxy C-5
description:
National Geographic series, "Megastructures," Mega Plane. 

The Galaxy C-5 is one of the largest U.S Airforce supply/carrier plane. 

The C-5 can carry fully equipped combat-ready military units to any point in the world on short notice and then provide field support required to help sustain the fighting force. (http://www.af.mil/factsheets/factsheet.asp?id=84)
